      "created_at": "2021-11-17T14:47:41.857Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Chriss, we are not planning AppleTV at this time.  We are small and testing each new device is very time consuming.  I would likely do windows before Apple TV but definitly when we get bigger and can afford more testers and devices we would consider it.  People are mirroring their phone or tablet to their AppleTV now.</p>",
