      "created_at": "2024-11-18T07:52:36.270Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes we really want to build a PC version or at least a web version that can run completely on PC/mac.  We decided AppleTV is too hard for now because the right bluetooth libraries don\u2019t exist.</p>",
