      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/bbe5ce/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2024-11-18T17:15:30.790Z",
      "cooked": "<p>It\u2019s probably just my need, but I find that following the training from a PC (with a dedicated app or a web version) is more convenient. With other training apps I use the Ant+ dongles which in my opinion cause fewer conflict problems than the BT. In any case, thank you for the effort you are making to try to satisfy users.</p>",
