      "name": "",
      "username": "Alex",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2024-11-18T17:36:59.037Z",
      "cooked": "<p>No it\u2019s not just you.  Anyone that has gotten used to using a PC from Zwift or TR or where ever has this thing dialed.  Sadly a web version could not support Ant+  even because we are using a layer on top of native programming developing an Ant+ library would be pretty costly even for a PC version.  We do what we can to keep our costs way down and remain ultra affordable yet profitable (soon\u2026) <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">  but yes a PC version with Ant+ would be the ultimate.  We just need to be a lot bigger first.</p>",
