      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2024-11-28T07:49:43.033Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Brian, we researched it as we like this option also.  It is harder than we hoped so we need to get bigger first.  One issue is we have a lot more Europeans than US folks and so AppleTV adoption is much lower in Europe so a PC would be a much bigger user base to support.  It\u2019s probably 20 to 1 as far as requests go.  But again we like AppleTV, I have one, I agree on everything you said it\u2019s just we are smaller and low cost so we have to be very careful how we prioritize stuff.</p>",
